<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h2>🎁 Your Order is Ready!</h2>
  <p>Order <strong><%= order.publicId %></strong> has been completed.</p>
  <div style="background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Your Product:</h3>
    <pre style="background: #18181b; color: #86efac; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= deliveredContent %></pre>
  </div>
  <p>You can also view your order at: <a href="<%= storeUrl %>/order/<%= order.publicId %>">Check Order</a></p>
  <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px;">Powered by Sellox</p>
</body>
</html>
